"title": "8344: servanthood, in life of believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8344: servanthood, in life of believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Servanthood as an expression of subservience is an integral aspect of a person's relationship with God.</p>\n<h2>Servants of God in the OT</h2>\n<h3>Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:5\">GEN 18:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:24\">GEN 26:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:27\">DEU 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:6\">PSA 105:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:42\">PSA 105:42</a></p>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:31\">EXO 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7-Num12:8\">NUM 12:7–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:5\">DEU 34:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:1-Josh1:2\">JOS 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:7\">JOS 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:13\">JOS 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:15\">JOS 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:31\">JOS 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:33\">JOS 8:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:15\">JOS 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:2\">JOS 22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:4-Josh22:5\">JOS 22:4–22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:12\">2KI 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:3\">2CH 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:5\">HEB 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>Joshua</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:8\">JDG 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:29\">JOS 24:29</a></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:18\">2SA 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5\">2SA 7:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:4\">1CH 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:8\">2SA 7:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:7\">1CH 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:18-2Sam7:20\">2SA 7:18–7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:25\">2SA 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:8\">1CH 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:70\">PSA 78:70</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:3\">PSA 89:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:20\">PSA 89:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:10\">PSA 132:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:23-Ezek34:24\">EZK 34:23–34:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69\">LUK 1:69</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:25-Acts4:26\">ACT 4:25–4:26</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ and servanthood</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's teaching on servanthood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:31–25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13-John13:17\">JHN 13:13–13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a></p>\n<h3>Parables on servanthood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:1-Matt20:16\">MAT 20:1–20:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:45-Matt24:51\">MAT 24:45–24:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:42-Luke12:46\">LUK 12:42–12:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:14–25:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12-Luke19:27\">LUK 19:12–19:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:35-Luke12:40\">LUK 12:35–12:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:7-Luke17:10\">LUK 17:7–17:10</a></p>\n<h2>Servants of God in the NT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:17\">ACT 16:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:18\">ACT 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29\">ACT 4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1\">2PE 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:1\">JUD 1:1</a></p>\n<h2>Paul as a servant</h2>\n<h3>A servant of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:17\">ROM 15:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9\">ROM 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:4\">2CO 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:3\">2TI 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>A servant of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1\">ROM 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:10\">GAL 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1\">PHP 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>A servant of the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:7\">EPH 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:23\">COL 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>A servant of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:5\">2CO 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24-Col1:25\">COL 1:24–1:25</a></p>\n<h2>Christian servanthood</h2>\n<h3>Gifts of service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10\">1PE 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:7\">ROM 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:5\">1CO 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">EPH 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:16\">1PE 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:11\">ROM 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:12-2Cor9:13\">2CO 9:12–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:6-Eph6:7\">EPH 6:6–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22-Col3:24\">COL 3:22–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Christian leadership entails service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:2-Acts6:41\">ACT 6:2–6:41</a>TI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:10\">3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:12-1Tim3:13\">1TI 3:12–3:13</a></p>",
